# POSMall Repository License

This repository is publicly visible, but it is not a public-domain package and
it is not released for standalone resale or redistribution.

## License Map

- Original POSMall additions created by KodZero / POSMall contributors are
  governed by the POSMall Personal-Use Non-Resale License in
  `LICENSE-POSMALL.md`.
- WingsOfWin demo catalog and demo business assets are governed by
  `LICENSE-WINGSOFWIN-DEMO-CONTENT.md`.
- Fork-origin portions from OFFLINE.Mall by OFFLINE GmbH and third-party
  packages keep their own upstream notices and licenses. The fork-origin notice is preserved in
  `THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES/OFFLINE-MALL-LICENSE.md`.

Read `LICENSING.md` for the full license map.

## POSMall Additions

Original POSMall additions include PostgreSQL-first architecture additions,
API/GraphQL additions, documentation, benchmark materials, seed examples, demo
business content, UI/business-flow additions, theme integration materials and
other original POSMall work.

These additions may be used for personal projects, internal projects, client
implementation/support work and operating a real website or application.

They may not be resold, sublicensed, redistributed, published, extracted or
packaged as a standalone product, marketplace item, plugin, theme, starter kit,
source package, architecture pack, API example pack, benchmark package or
competing package.

## Fork-Origin Notice

The fork-origin notice for OFFLINE.Mall by OFFLINE GmbH is preserved in
`THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES/OFFLINE-MALL-LICENSE.md` for attribution and license
continuity of fork-origin portions only.

That upstream notice does not license original POSMall additions for standalone
resale, redistribution or repackaging.

POSMall does not claim ownership of fork-origin code. POSMall claims ownership
and applies this repository's non-resale terms only to original POSMall
additions and POSMall-owned materials.
